{"site": {"media": "/media", "year": 2014, "template_engine": null, "date": "2014-10-15T12-36-15", "lux_version": "0.1.1-alpha.1", "url": "http://quantmind.github.io/lux", "name": "Lux", "template": "doc.html", "python_version": "3.4.1"}, "slug": "api/static", "api_url": "http://quantmind.github.io/lux/jsonapi/docs/api/static", "head": {}, "modified": "2014-03-27T17:02:36", "html": {"main": "<section id=\"page-header\" class=\"page-header-outer api_static-header\">\n    <div class=\"layer\">\n        <div class=\"page-header\">\n            <div class=\"container fullpage\">\n                <div class=\"row fullpage\">\n                    <div class=\"col-sm-12 text-center\">\n                        <breadcrumbs></breadcrumbs>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>\n\n<div id=\"page-main\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"api_static-main col-md-12\">\n                <div class=\"center-block\" style=\"max-width: 900px\" data-highlight data-hash-scroll>\n                    <div class=\"section\" id=\"module-lux.extensions.static\">\n<span id=\"static-site-builder\"></span><span id=\"extension-static\"></span><h1>Static site builder<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#module-lux.extensions.static\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h1>\n<p>Static site generator</p>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"usage\">\n<h2>Usage<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#usage\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h2>\n<p>Put the <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#module-lux.extensions.static\" title=\"lux.extensions.static\"><tt class=\"xref py py-mod docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">lux.extensions.static</span></tt></a> extension into your <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"params#std:setting-EXTENSIONS\"><tt class=\"xref std std-setting docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">EXTENSIONS</span></tt></a>\nlist and build the static web site via the <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">build_static</span></tt> option in the\ncommand line:</p>\n<div class=\"highlight-python\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre>python managet.py build_static\n</pre></div>\n</div>\n<p>There are several <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"params#parameters-static\"><em>parameters</em></a> which can be modified\nin order to customise the site.</p>\n<p>The first step is to create a new project via the <strong class=\"command\">create_project</strong></p>\n<p>When creating the middleware for the static site one can pass the following\nkey-valued parameters during initialisation of a <tt class=\"xref py py-class docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">HtmlContent</span></tt>,\na <tt class=\"xref py py-class docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">Blog</span></tt> and other routers:</p>\n<ul class=\"simple\">\n<li><tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">dir</span></tt> the directory where the source files are located, if not provided,\nit is assumed it is the same as the route parameter</li>\n<li><tt class=\"xref py py-attr docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">html_body_template</span></tt> to specify the\nlocation of the template which render the html body tag of the Html5\ndocument. If not provided, the parent router value is used unless no parent\nis available and the <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"params#std:setting-STATIC_TEMPLATE\"><tt class=\"xref std std-setting docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">STATIC_TEMPLATE</span></tt></a> is used instead.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<div class='small hidden-print text-muted' id='page-footer'>\n    <div class='container'>\n        <div class='row'>\n            <div class='block col-sm-5'>\n                <div class='hidden-xs'>\n                    <ul class=\"fa-ul text-left\">\n    <li><i class=\"fa-li fa fa-copyright\"></i>2014 <a href=\"http://quantmind.com\">Quantmind</a></li>\n    <li>Site build with Lux on python 3.4.1</li>\n    <li>Docs build with <a href=\"http://sphinx-doc.org/\" target=\"_blank\">Sphinx</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"http://quantmind.github.io/lux/docs/changelog\">Changelog</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"http://quantmind.github.io/lux/docs/api/\">API</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"http://quantmind.github.io/lux/docs/EXTENSIONS/\">Extensions</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"http://quantmind.github.io/lux/images\">Images</a></li>\n</ul>\n                </div>\n                <div class='text-center visible-xs'>\n                    <ul class=\"fa-ul text-left\">\n    <li><i class=\"fa-li fa fa-copyright\"></i>2014 <a href=\"http://quantmind.com\">Quantmind</a></li>\n    <li>Site build with Lux on python 3.4.1</li>\n    <li>Docs build with <a href=\"http://sphinx-doc.org/\" target=\"_blank\">Sphinx</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"http://quantmind.github.io/lux/docs/changelog\">Changelog</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"http://quantmind.github.io/lux/docs/api/\">API</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"http://quantmind.github.io/lux/docs/EXTENSIONS/\">Extensions</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"http://quantmind.github.io/lux/images\">Images</a></li>\n</ul>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class='block col-sm-2 text-center'>\n                <div class='hidden-xs'>\n                    <p><a href='#top' title=\"Lux\" class=\"hover-opacity\">\n    <img height=50 title='Lux' src='http://quantmind.github.io/lux/media/luxsite/lux.png' alt='Lux'>\n</a></p>\n                </div>\n                <div class='visible-xs'>\n                    <p><a href='https://twitter.com/quantmind' title='Follow quantmind on twitter'>\n<i class='fa fa-twitter fa-2x'></i></a>\n<a href='https://plus.google.com/+QuantmindPlus' title='Follow quantmind on google+'>\n<i class='fa fa-google-plus-square fa-2x'></i></a>\n<a href='https://www.facebook.com/quantmind' title='Follow quantmind on facebook'>\n<i class='fa fa-facebo